
Ranger Help for: forest
=======================

SUMMARY:    
The forest is probably the most well known Ranger setting. Its wooded,
with a temperate climate and an abundance of life. Almost all Ranger skills
will work in the forest terrain, so no doubt, a lot of Rangers will be forest
Rangers.  Forests abound in Darkwind and in Kerei. 

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: Individual terrains

